@startmindmap UEORMS_Navigation_Part_1
title UEORMS Navigation Chart - Part 1: Access and Navigation Foundations

skinparam monochrome false
skinparam defaultFontName Courier


* UEORMS Navigation Chart
** Evidence Sources (Current System)
*** frontend/src/App.jsx (exact route inventory)
*** frontend/src/components/layout/Sidebar.jsx (role + module gated menus)
*** frontend/src/pages/Dashboard.jsx (role to dashboard resolver)
*** frontend/src/auth/Login.jsx (billing check and redirect)
*** frontend/src/auth/ProtectedRoute.jsx (auth guard and redirect)
*** report/old_project_report_extracted.txt (report intent context)
** Entry and Access Flow
*** Public Routes (6)
**** /
**** /login
**** /register
**** /forgot-password
**** /accept-invite
**** /theme-demo
*** Login Processing
**** Submit credentials -> loginApi
**** Persist token
**** Query /billing/subscription
***** ACTIVE or unknown -> /dashboard
***** NON_ACTIVE -> /subscription/billing
*** Protected Route Guard
**** if authenticated -> render target page
**** if unauthenticated -> redirect to /
** Dashboard Hub
*** Route: /dashboard
*** Role-to-dashboard mapping
**** ADMIN -> AdminDashboard
**** MANAGER -> ManagerDashboard
**** HR_MANAGER -> HRManagerDashboard
**** HR_STAFF -> HRStaffDashboard
**** FINANCE_MANAGER -> FinanceManagerDashboard
**** ACCOUNTANT -> AccountantDashboard
**** INVENTORY_MANAGER -> InventoryManagerDashboard
**** WAREHOUSE_STAFF -> WarehouseStaffDashboard
**** SALES_MANAGER -> SalesManagerDashboard
**** SALES_STAFF -> SalesStaffDashboard
**** PURCHASE_MANAGER -> PurchaseManagerDashboard
**** PROJECT_MANAGER -> ProjectManagerDashboard
**** EMPLOYEE -> EmployeeDashboard
**** USER -> UserDashboard
** Sidebar Menu Resolution
*** Input controls
**** user.role
**** company enabledModules
**** duplicate path elimination (Map by path)
*** Role-based menu segments
**** HR roles -> HR, attendance, leave, payroll
**** Finance roles -> finance, accounting, approvals
**** Inventory roles -> inventory, warehouse, receipts, dispatch
**** Sales roles -> CRM, sales orders, quotations, analytics
**** Purchase roles -> vendors, orders, requisitions, analytics
**** PM/Manager roles -> projects, tasks, approvals, reports
**** EMPLOYEE -> self-service views
**** USER -> basic inventory/docs/messages/notifications
**** ADMIN -> role-management, roles, company, system-options, audit

@endmindmap
